## 1. How to Use This Roadmap <a name="how-to-use"></a>

- **Learn → Build → Review → Practice** — follow this cycle each week
- Mark each topic ✅ as you complete it
- For every concept, ask: *"How would I explain this in an interview in under 2 minutes?"*
- Do at least **2 mock system design interviews** per week after Phase 2
- Keep a personal **"Design Journal"** — write one-pager designs for every problem you solve

